<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logo1.png" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="File not found on BurnLink. The link may be malformed or the file has already been downloaded." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
  <title>File Not Found - BurnLink</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; line-height: 1.6; overflow-x: hidden; min-height: 100vh; }
    .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
    header { padding: 1.75rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e1e; position: sticky; top: 0; background: #0a0a0a; z-index: 100; }
    .header-content { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .logo { text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .logo img { height: 45px; width: auto; display: block; }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; }
    nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #666; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; }
    nav a:hover, nav a.active { color: #fff; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding: 3rem 0; }
    .footer-content { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .footer-section h3 { font-size: 0.68rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #555; }
    .footer-section a { display: block; color: #777; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-section a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid #1e1e1e; padding-top: 1.5rem; color: #444; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    main { padding: 8rem 0 4rem; min-height: calc(100vh - 140px); display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .error-wrap { max-width: 520px; }
    .error-code { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #ff8c00; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -1.5px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
    .btn-primary { background: #ff8c00; color: #000; }
    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: #aaa; border: 1px solid #333; }
    .btn:hover { opacity: 0.8; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { gap: 1.5rem; }
      .header-content { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
      .footer-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
      main { padding: 4rem 0 2rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 1.85rem; }
      .btn-row { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn { text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
  <script defer src="https://cloud.umami.is/script.js" data-website-id="5557b587-f2e2-4eb6-8edd-582164ff68da"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header-content">
        <a href="/" class="logo"><img src="/logo1.png" alt="BurnLink" /></a>
        <nav><a href="/">Home</a><a href="/about">About</a><a href="/security-policy">Security policy</a></nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="error-wrap">
        <p class="error-code">404 — Not Found</p>
        <h1>File not found.</h1>
        <p>The file was not found, the link may be malformed, or it has already been downloaded once. BurnLink links are single-use.</p>
        <div class="btn-row">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Share a new file</a>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-ghost">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Product</h3>
          <a href="/">Share files</a>
          <a href="/about">How it works</a>
          <a href="/security-policy">Security policy</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Security</h3>
          <a href="/security-policy">Security policy</a>
          <a href="/hall-of-fame">Hall of fame</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-section">
          <h3>Developer</h3>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Joy G. Majumdar</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/Joy-Majumder/BurnLink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://paperfrogs.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Paperfrogs Lab</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 BurnLink &mdash; A product of <a href="https://paperfrogs.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color:#555;text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#fff'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#555'">Paperfrogs Lab</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>